Nivatech Delivery Privacy Policy

1. Introduction
Welcome to Nivatech Market, a service of Nivatech. Your privacy is our priority. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you use our multi-vendor platform.

2. Information We Collect
2.1 Information Provided by the User

Registration Information: Name, email address, phone number, physical address.
Payment Information: Credit card details or other billing information.
2.2 Information Collected Automatically

Browsing Data: IP address, device information, browser type, pages visited, duration of visit.
Cookies and Similar Technologies: We use cookies to enhance your user experience and track your preferences.
3. Use of Information
We use your information to:

Provide and Improve Our Services: Process transactions, customer service, and personalize user experience.
Security: Prevent fraud and protect our users.
Marketing and Communication: Send newsletters, special offers, and product updates (with your explicit consent).
4. Sharing of Information
We only share your personal information with third parties in the following situations:

Third-Party Sellers: To process your orders and deliveries.
Service Providers: Including payment processors, hosting services, and other technical providers.
Legal Compliance: To comply with legal obligations or protect our rights.
5. Information Security
We implement technical and organizational measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. All data is transmitted securely using modern encryption (e.g., HTTPS).

6. Your Rights
You have the following rights regarding your personal information:

Access: Request access to your personal information.
Correction: Request correction of any inaccurate information.
Deletion: Request deletion of your personal information under certain conditions.
Withdraw Consent: Withdraw your consent at any time where we rely on your consent to process your information.
7. Cookies
We use cookies to improve your experience on our site. You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings. For detailed information, please refer to our Cookie Policy.

8. Changes to the Privacy Policy
We may update this privacy policy periodically. Significant changes will be communicated through notifications on our site, and the revision date will be updated accordingly.

9. Contact Us
For questions or concerns regarding this privacy policy, please contact us at:

Email: info@nivatech.elementfx.com
Address: Nivatech, 1 Ronelle Street, Haazandal, Brackenfell, 7560.
Revision Date: July 15, 2024

